00986 BOOLEAN ReadInItemStats(STR fileName, BOOLEAN localizedVersion )
00987 {
00988       HWFILE            hFile;
00989       UINT32            uiBytesRead;
00990       UINT32            uiFSize;
00991       CHAR8 *           lpcBuffer;
00992       XML_Parser  parser = XML_ParserCreate(NULL);
00993       
00994       itemParseData pData;
00995       
00996       localizedTextOnly = localizedVersion;
00997 
00998       DebugMsg(TOPIC_JA2, DBG_LEVEL_3, "Loading Items.xml" );
00999 
01000       // Open items file
01001       hFile = FileOpen( fileName, FILE_ACCESS_READ, FALSE );
01002       if ( !hFile )
01003             return( FALSE );
01004       
01005       uiFSize = FileGetSize(hFile);
01006       lpcBuffer = (CHAR8 *) MemAlloc(uiFSize+1);
01007 
01008       //Read in block
01009       if ( !FileRead( hFile, lpcBuffer, uiFSize, &uiBytesRead ) )
